{"tid":2124540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"細談一下我鐘意左 金珉周 之後的神奇變化","createTime":"2020-07-25T12:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T07:43:26.000Z","uid":256952,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b5773033af482a51c55574f40a1cf80253717b57","tid":2124540,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"由303排第11名到依家可以成為C位嘅珉周<br />\n突然感慨一下<br />\n珉周係我第一個鍾意的女人 <br />\n一開始追Produce 48嗰陣對佢實在冇乜印象 直到我見到了佢呢條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hmPazW6utms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhmPazW6utms&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=2bcddb69\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hmPazW6utms</a><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣我就喺度諗 呢個女仔都幾冇偶像包袱得來又幾真<br />\n我覺得珉周由一開始嘅冇乜自信到今時今日C位佢真係出左唔少力，雖然佢一開始就背負着同支魚嘅外貌相似先出到道，但係其實我覺得佢一啲都唔似周支魚。minju 有自己獨特嘅外貌特徵係同其他人唔同嘅<br />\n<br />\n我鐘意周周之前 我人生冇咩目標 個樣都唔係幾靚仔<br />\n所以自信心特別低 成日都比同學蝦<br />\n至從留意左周周之後 成個人精神哂 自信都開始黎番，連以前蝦我既蛋散 反而係我蝦返佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金珉周真係音樂界華陀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaXhF8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaXhF8s.jpg&h=d181ca22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEykDVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEykDVc.jpg&h=ff09e543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAYQgJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAYQgJg.jpg&h=816f6da1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d72e5f5d36ce36ab005d97a866fd1acc39f28fb8","tid":2124540,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3b0ff927185c6cf2e3ea12dd90e3eec6856229","tid":2124540,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:41:48.00